high_descs: Turn around, go between the white shelves and the large white table, and turn to face the large white table.
Pick up the key ring from the white table.
Turn right, go to the dark gray couch, turn left, go to the other end of the dark gray couch, turn in a circle and face the dark gray couch.
Place the key ring on the left cushion of the dark gray couch.
Turn left and go to the small white table.
Pick up the key ring from the small white table.
Turn around and go to the dark gray couch.
Place the key ring on the left cushion of the dark gray couch.
anns.task_desc: Place two key rings on the dark gray couch.

high_descs: Move to the coffee table in the middle of the room.
PIck up the keys from the table.
Move to the couch to the right of the door.
Place the keys on the couch on the left side.
Move to the end table to the right of the couch behind and to the right of you.
Pick up the keys from the end table.
Move to the couch where the keys placed from before are.
Place the keys next to the previous set of keys.
anns.task_desc: Put two sets of keys on the couch cushion closet to the door.

high_descs: Walk to the table
Pick the keys up from the table
Carry them to the couch
Set them down on the couch cushion
Walk back to the table
Grab the other set of keys from the table
Carry them to the couch
Set them down on the couch cushion
anns.task_desc: Getting the keys to the couch

high_descs: Turn left, go straight, at the white side table turn left, go straight past the coffee table, turn right, go straight, turn right toward the coffee table.
Take the keys from the coffee table.
Turn right, go straight, go forward and left to the left side of the couch.
Put the keys on the left couch cushion at the center edge.
Turn left, go straight to the white side table.
Take the keys to the side table.
Turn around, go straight, turn left to face the left side of the couch.
Put the keys to the right of the first keys on the couch cushion.
anns.task_desc: Put two keys on a couch.
